            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEcclesiastes%207%3A1-9%3A18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEcclesiastes%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EWisdom%20for%20Life%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20good%20reputation%20is%20more%20valuable%20than%20costly%20perfume.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAnd%20the%20day%20you%20die%20is%20better%20than%20the%20day%20you%20are%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EBetter%20to%20spend%20your%20time%20at%20funerals%20than%20at%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAfter%20all%2C%20everyone%20dies%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20the%20living%20should%20take%20this%20to%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESorrow%20is%20better%20than%20laughter%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20sadness%20has%20a%20refining%20influence%20on%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_4%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20wise%20person%20thinks%20a%20lot%20about%20death%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhile%20a%20fool%20thinks%20only%20about%20having%20a%20good%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_5%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EBetter%20to%20be%20criticized%20by%20a%20wise%20person%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethan%20to%20be%20praised%20by%20a%20fool.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_6%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20fool%26%23x2019%3Bs%20laughter%20is%20quickly%20gone%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20thorns%20crackling%20in%20a%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThis%20also%20is%20meaningless.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_7%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EExtortion%20turns%20wise%20people%20into%20fools%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20bribes%20corrupt%20the%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_8%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EFinishing%20is%20better%20than%20starting.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EPatience%20is%20better%20than%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_9%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EControl%20your%20temper%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20anger%20labels%20you%20a%20fool.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_10%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20long%20for%20%26%23x201C%3Bthe%20good%20old%20days.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThis%20is%20not%20wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_11%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EWisdom%20is%20even%20better%20when%20you%20have%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBoth%20are%20a%20benefit%20as%20you%20go%20through%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_12%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EWisdom%20and%20money%20can%20get%20you%20almost%20anything%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20only%20wisdom%20can%20save%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_13%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EAccept%20the%20way%20God%20does%20things%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20who%20can%20straighten%20what%20he%20has%20made%20crooked%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_14%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EEnjoy%20prosperity%20while%20you%20can%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20when%20hard%20times%20strike%2C%20realize%20that%20both%20come%20from%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ERemember%20that%20nothing%20is%20certain%20in%20this%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22eccl_7_15%22%20bk%3D%22eccl%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Limits%20of%20Human%20Wisdom%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20seen%20everything%20in%20this%20meaningless%20life%2C%20including%20the%20death%20of%20good%20young%20people%20and%20the%20